	* mel-b-ccl.el (mel-ccl-decode-b): Check `ccl-cascading-read' to
	select implementation.

1998-11-12  Tanaka Akira  <akr@jaist.ac.jp>

	* mel-q-ccl.el (mel-ccl-encode-quoted-printable-generic): workaround 
	for mule-2.3@19.34.

